Sentencas: The anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated and joined onto the metal cap (SUS430) for current collecting and sealing by using the induction brazing process.
Titulo: Joining of Metallic Cap and Anode-Supported Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell by Induction Brazing Process
